Supplied in a 2M coil, this insulation has very low thermal conductivity alongside high levels of resistance to water vapour transmission, helping to reduce energy losses during the long term while also minimising moisture ingress and reducing the risk of corrosion under insulation (CUI). Suitable for installation in public buildings and for use in process industries, AF Evo has inbuilt antimicrobial protection and high levels of fire performance make it a reliable choice for even the most challenging of situations. In addition to insulation, the AF/Armaflex range includes fire sleeves, pipe supports and adhesives for a comprehensive single-brand solution.

Title: Charles Austen Pumps Mini Blue X87-504 pump temperature sensor
Description: The whisper-quiet Charles Austen Pumps MiniBlue condensate removal pump with temperature sensor offers 8L/h flow rates for the reliable removal of condensate and debris. This self-priming pump provides peristaltic performance at the price of a piston pump and is small enough for fast installation or retrofit into any existing installation. Using BlueDiamond patented rotary diaphragm technology, the MiniBlue draws in condensate using vacuum and mechanically driven technology in a reinforced elastomer diaphragm, directing it to the outlet under pressure. Able to run dry, this system tolerates suspended solids and light slurries for reliable use in tough conditions.

Supplied in a 15M coil, this insulation has very low thermal conductivity alongside high levels of resistance to water vapour transmission, helping to reduce energy losses during the long term while also minimising moisture ingress and reducing the risk of corrosion under insulation (CUI). Suitable for installation in public buildings and for use in process industries, AF Evo has inbuilt antimicrobial protection and high levels of fire performance make it a reliable choice for even the most challenging of situations. In addition to insulation, the AF/Armaflex range includes fire sleeves, pipe supports and adhesives for a comprehensive single-brand solution.
